modules.script:
def row_extender(data, id):
    for index,x in enumerate(data["X"].replace(" ", "")):
        data[f"{index+1}X"] = x    
    for index,x in enumerate(data["Y"].replace(" ", "")):
        data[f"{index+1}Y"] = x
    
    prices = []

    def get_price(key="", key_text="", column="", check_price=0, uncheck_price=0, data=data, price=prices):
        if key_text in data.get(column,""):
            data[key] = "☑️"
            prices.append(check_price)
        else:
            data[key] = "☐"
            prices.append(uncheck_price)


    get_price("1EC", "Ja", "AA", -5)
    get_price("2EC", "Ja", "AB", 0, 20)
